metadata.description:
Play Senatry at http://senatry.lekool.com
Senatry is a free web browser mmo created in the genre of real-time strategy and combat.
Set in the Old Roman Empire, Senatry allows you to role play as a strategist, and your task is to rewrite history to restore the glory of Rome. Expand your city, upgrade your heroes, recruit commanders, train armies conquer lands and forge your own empire. Fight against other players and monsters in a real-time strategy Senatry.
